arts.ttl: Real Salt Lake ties St. Louis City 2-2 to earn final postseason spot in Western Conference
arts.sum: Jo√£o Klauss scored in the 88th minute and St. Louis City rallied to tie Real Salt Lake 2-2 to close out the regular season on Saturday night. Klauss matched his career high with his 10th goal of the season for St. Louis City (8-18-8).
